Text: CongratulationsGeneral Whalley Kept thinking I would see you around outside to tell you personally how excited I was to hear of your promotion Just wanted to take a moment to tell you how proud I am of you and your accomplishments I knew you would do a great job for Enron when Lloyd and I moved you here Little did I know How well It does my heart good to see someone of your calibre come into a new Corporate environment and progress to such heights Belated Congratulations Deborah Kallus Enron Relocation Consultant
